Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:12.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サスケ)守る… 守るだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:17.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんの冗談だ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:19.85,japanese,,0,0,0,,(マダラ)もう一度 言う。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:23.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前は 兄のことを\N知っているようで何も知らない。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:29.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,それ以上 ふざけたことを\Nぬかせば お前を殺す。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:33.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうやら ひと筋縄では\Nいかなそうだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.54,0:00:36.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,まあ ムリもない。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:40.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,怪しげなヤツに\Nこんなことを急に言われてもな。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:44.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが オレの話していることは事実。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:49.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,イタチからも聞いただろう？\Nあの夜の協力者のことを。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:55.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレが その うちはマダラだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:02.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,イタチのことなら\Nなんでも知っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:06.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,まあ イタチは そのことに\N気づかずに死んだがな。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:11.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,うるせぇ!! そんなことは\Nもう どうだっていい！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:13.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレの前から消えろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:17.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,いや 聞いてもらう。\Nお前は 聞かなくてはならない。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.90,0:01:20.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,それが お前の義務だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:26.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,忍の世のため\N木ノ葉のため そして何より➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:29.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,弟のお前のために\Nすべてを懸けた兄➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.92,0:01:32.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,うちはイタチの生きざまを。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.27,0:01:40.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,わかるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:44.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,イタチが なぜ お前の眼に\N天照を仕込んだか。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:46.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハア… ハア… ハア…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:51.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前とオレを イタチは どうしても\N引き合わせたくなかったからだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:55.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,その理由は\Nオレの話を聞けば すべてわかる。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:03.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,イタチの真実を知る者は\N木ノ葉のダンゾウと三代目 火影➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:09.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして 相談役の２人\Nホムラとコハルの４人だけだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:15.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,三代目が死に 今\Nそれを知るのは年寄りばかり３人。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.41,0:02:18.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヤツらは これから先も絶対に➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:21.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,あの忌まわしい事実を\N口外しないだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:25.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,イタチの真実は 永久に闇へと消える。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:29.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして イタチも それを望んでいた。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:36.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが オレも\Nイタチの真実を知っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:39.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,さっきも言ったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:43.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,イタチは そのことについては\N気づかずに死んだと。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:49.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,しかし 念には念… イタチは\Nオレを信用していなかったようだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:52.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,万に一つ その真実を\N知るやもしれぬと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:56.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,天照で オレの口を閉ざそうとした。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:58.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前と話をするために➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:02.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレが写輪眼を見せることまで\N計算していたんだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:08.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,何を言ってる…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:11.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,何を言ってんだ？ コイツ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:20.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレを守る… 守る？ 真実… だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:26.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,思い出せ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:32.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,イタチのことを\Nゆっくりと思い出してみろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:45.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハア… ハア… ハア…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:48.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前の優しかった兄を…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:05.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,((イタチ : どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:10.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,ここでしょ？\N父さんが働いてるところ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉警務部隊の本部だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:17.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,前から気になってたんだけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:22.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,何で 警務部隊のマークに\Nうちは一族の家紋が入ってるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:25.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんだ 気づいてたのか？\N当たり前だろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:29.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,うん そうだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:33.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,簡単に言うと\Nこの警務部隊を組織し➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:36.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,設立したのが うちは一族の\N先代たちだったらしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:41.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,だからこの組織のシンボルマークに\N自分たちの家紋をつけたのさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:47.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,昔からうちは一族は この里の\N治安をずっと預かり守ってきた。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:52.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,うちはの家紋は その誇り高き\N一族の証しでもあるんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:57.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,今や うちは一族も\N小さくなってしまったけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:05:01.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,今でもほぼ全員が\Nここの第一分隊に所属し➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:03.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,里の治安維持に貢献している。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:08.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,忍の起こす犯罪を\N取り締まれるのは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:11.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,更に 優秀な忍だけだからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:14.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,《やっぱり父さんはすごいや》
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,兄さんもここに入るの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:19.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,さあ どうかな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:21.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,(そうしなよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:30.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,いや アイツは アイツは\Nオレを殺そうとしたじゃないか！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレの眼を奪おうと。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,((誰がこんなことを！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:43.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,愚かなる弟よ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:45.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,(万華鏡写輪眼！))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:04.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,落ち着け。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:06.64,japanese,,0,0,0,,ゆっくり息をしろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレに触るな！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:26.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,((例え 憎まれようともな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:29.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,(それが兄貴ってもんだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:37.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,((許せ サスケ。 また今度だ))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:38.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,気がついたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:41.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,悪いが 拘束させてもらった。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:44.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,おとなしく 話を聞いて\Nもらえそうもなかったからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:53.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,アイツは… イタチは敵だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:58.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,父さんと母さんを殺し\N一族を皆殺しに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:02.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,抜け忍で… 暁のメンバーだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:06.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,アイツは憎むべき存在だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:09.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレの目的…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:14.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,あの夜… ヤツが うちは一族を\N皆殺しにしたのは 事実だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:17.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして 木ノ葉を抜けた。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:19.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,だったら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:24.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして そうすることが\N木ノ葉から下された任務だった。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:30.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,それが イタチの真実への入り口だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:32.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,任務だと!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:38.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,そうだ。 あの夜 イタチは己を殺し\N任務をやり遂げたのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:46.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,少し 落ち着いたようだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:48.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,イタチの話をするには➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:55.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉創立の時代まで\N話をさかのぼらねばならない。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:00.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,イタチは犠牲になったのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:05.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,古くから続く因縁…\Nその犠牲にな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:08.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,犠牲？\Nそうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:13.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,そもそもが 木ノ葉隠れの里が\N生まれたときからある➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:18.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,大きな問題だ。\Nそれが イタチの生き様を決めた。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:24.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,少し 長い話になるが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:27.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,これから話すことは\Nすべて事実だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:32.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,何を根拠に信じろと？\Nお前は信用できない。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:36.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,提示できる証拠はない。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:39.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレの話を信じるかどうかは\Nお前が決めればいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:43.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが 話は 最後まで聞いてもらう。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:58.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,いいだろう。 話せ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,フッ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:04.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,今より 80年以上も前の話だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:13.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,(マダラ)かつて 世界は\N戦いの絶えない 戦国時代だった。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:16.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,国々は 自国の利権や➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:20.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,領土拡大のために\N争いを続けていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:26.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,その戦乱の時代… 忍の組織は\N一族単位の武装集団でしかなく➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:32.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,それぞれの一族は国に雇われ\N戦争に参加していた。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:36.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして その数多くの\N忍一族の中にあって➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:40.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,最強と恐れられた\N二つの一族があった。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:44.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,それが 我らが うちは一族と➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:48.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,森の千手一族と呼ばれる\N一族だった。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:52.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,我ら うちは一族は\N頭抜けたチャクラと写輪眼を有し➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:56.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,あらゆる戦闘に長けた\Nいわゆる 戦闘一族として➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:59.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,知れ渡っていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:02.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして オレは\Nその うちは一族の中でも➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:06.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,特別に強いチャクラを持つ者として\N生まれた。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:11.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,しぶとく生き長らえているのが\Nその証といってもいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:15.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,かつてのオレは\N戦いに明け暮れていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:17.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,力が ものをいう時代。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:23.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは より強い力を求め\N友も弟も この手にかけた。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:26.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,キサマ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:30.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが そのおかげで\N完全なる万華鏡を手に入れ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:33.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは うちはのリーダーとなった。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:38.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして その力を使い\N幾度となく 千手一族と戦った。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:42.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,千手一族の長…\N柱間を相手にするには➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,仕方のないことだったのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:51.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,後に 初代火影となる\N木遁の千手柱間…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:55.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,この忍の世界の頂点であり\Nオレのあこがれの忍だった。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:07.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,(マダラ)火影の名を初めて名乗った男\N柱間が率いる千手一族は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:13.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,どの忍一族からも一目置かれ\N何より恐れられていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:17.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,千手が動けば うちはが動く。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:21.85,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヤツらを相手にできるのは\N我が一族ぐらいのものだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:25.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,千手を雇えば\N対立国は うちはを雇う。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:27.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,まるで ライバルだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:32.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,柱間と対立するうち オレの名も\Nどんどんと知られていった。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:40.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,((イタチ : 高みに近づくため\Nその器を量るためだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:43.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,名を上げる…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:47.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,そんなことのために\N弟の眼を奪ったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:53.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,奪った… だが それは\Nうちは一族を守るための力が➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:55.85,japanese,,0,0,0,,必要だったからだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,守るためだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:14:02.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,そう うちはの名が上がれば\Nおのずと敵も増える。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:05.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,激しい争いの中で➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:09.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,千手一族をはじめとする\N外敵から一族を守るには➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:12.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,必要な犠牲だった。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:15.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,名を上げるためではない。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:19.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,弟は すべて承知のうえだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:22.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,自ら眼を差し出したのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:29.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが あるとき\N千手一族は うちはに対して➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:32.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,休戦を申し出てきた。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:36.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,うちはは これに同意した。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:38.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,双方の一族の誰もが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:41.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,長く終わりのない戦いに\N疲れ切っていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:45.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,限界にきていたのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:50.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが オレは\N休戦に ただ一人 反対した。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:55.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,今までの憎しみは\Nどこに行ったというのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:59.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,弟は 何のために\N犠牲になったというのだ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:09.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,しょせん\Nうちはと千手は水と油だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:12.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,いずれ うちは一族は\N千手一族によって➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:15.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,駆逐されてしまう\Nそう思えてならなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:24.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが うちは一族の皆は\N休戦を望んでやまなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:30.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレはリーダーとして しかたなく\N皆の意志を汲み取った。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:33.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,それから ほどなく➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:37.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,我ら忍連合は\N領土の平定を望んでいた➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:40.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,火の国との協定に こぎつける。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:45.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,そこに一国一里の\N強固な組織ができあがった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:49.64,japanese,,0,0,0,,火の国と木ノ葉隠れの里だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:54.45,japanese,,0,0,0,,一国一里のシステムを\Nあらゆる国々が真似ていった。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:58.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,それにともない\N争いも徐々に鎮火していく。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:01.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,ひとたびの平和だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:03.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが 木ノ葉は\Nある出来事によって➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:06.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,すぐ混乱に陥った。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:09.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,ある出来事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:13.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,里長 初代火影の座をめぐる\N争いだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:20.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前も知るとおり\Nその座を得たのは 千手柱間だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:23.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,火の国も里の皆も柱間を選んだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:26.85,japanese,,0,0,0,,うちはが主権の座から\Nどんどんと遠ざかっていくのは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:28.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,明らかだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは うちはを守るため➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:34.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,うちは主導の道を\N選ぶことを決めた。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:38.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,柱間と対峙する道をいくことを…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.98,japanese,,0,0,0,,しかし うちはの者でさえ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:43.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレに ついてくる者は\Nいなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:46.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,部下たちは 再び争いの火種を➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:48.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,起こそうとする\Nオレをうとましく思い➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:51.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,裏切ったのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:59.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは 利己的な欲求に\N突き動かされていると叩かれ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:03.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,それどころか\N己の命を守るために➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:07.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,弟の眼を奪った\N欲深い兄だと さげすまれた。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:11.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,どこに好き好んで\N弟を傷つける兄がいる…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:15.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは ただ… うちはを\N守りたかっただけだというのに。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:23.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは 里を出た。\Nすべてに裏切られてな。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:29.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして 復讐者となり\N木ノ葉隠れの里に戦いを挑んだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:48.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,(マダラ)だが オレは敗れた。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:53.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,終末の谷と呼ばれるようになった\Nあの場所でな。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:56.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレはあそこで死んだとされている。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:18:00.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,柱間でさえ そう思ったはずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:07.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは 皆から そして 歴史から\N忘れ去られていった。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:10.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,柱間の弟である 二代目火影は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:13.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,二度と\Nオレのような反逆者を出さぬため➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:19.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,信頼の証しとして\Nうちはに 特別な役職を与えた。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:22.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉警務部隊の設立だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:28.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,しかし その実際は\N里の政から うちはを遠ざけ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:33.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,なおかつ 一族を ひとまとめに\N監視下に置くためのものだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:36.64,japanese,,0,0,0,,その意図に気づく\Nうちはの者もいた。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:41.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレの意志を継ぐ\N造反勢力も出てきた。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:44.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,が… 時 すでに遅し。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.32,0:18:49.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,時は流れ 主権は千手の手に。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:53.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,誇り高き うちは一族は\N千手の犬へと成り下がった。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:56.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして\Nオレの考えたとおりになった。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:19:00.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,ある事件で うちはは\N完全に駆逐されてしまう。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:11.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,そう…\N16年前の 九尾の妖狐 襲来だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:23.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,九尾を手なずけ コントロールすることが\Nできるのは うちはの瞳力だけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:26.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉の上役たちは あの事件を➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:30.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,うちはの何者かによる\Nしわざではないかと勘ぐった。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:34.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,あれは 自然発生的な\Nいわば 天災だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:36.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,うちはは関係していない。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:40.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが あらぬ疑いがかけられた。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:47.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,うちはが主権を狙って 反逆を\N起こそうとしたのではないか と。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:52.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,以降 うちはへの監視は\N暗部によって徹底され➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:56.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,一族の居住地は\N里の片隅へと追いやられ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,隔離さながらの状態になった。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:04.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,唯一 三代目火影だけは\Nその処置に異議を唱えたが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:10.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,暗部のダンゾウ そして 相談役たちは\Nそれを認めなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:15.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,しょせん うちは一族は\N信用されていなかったのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:18.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,差別が始まった。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:29.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヤツらの不信は わだかまりを生み\N疑いはやがて 現実となっていく。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:36.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,うちは一族は クーデターを企んだ。\N里を乗っ取るために…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:39.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして 木ノ葉上層部は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:43.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,うちは一族の中に\Nスパイを送り込んだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:47.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,それが お前の兄 うちはイタチだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:56.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,そこから\Nイタチの地獄は始まったのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:45.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,＜791年 ハルジオン港。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:49.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナツたちが天狼島で\N消息を絶ってから➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:54.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,すでに ７年の歳月が流れていた＞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:57.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ビスカ)いつまで海を見てるんだい。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.70,0:23:00.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,(アルザック)\N仕事も終わったし ギルドに戻ろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:09.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:12.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say protect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:16.58,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:19.51,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you know about your brother,\Nbut you know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:29.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue speaking\Nsuch nonsense, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:33.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not making this easy, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:36.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that's natural though...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:40.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly being told such a story\Nby a stranger like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:44.71,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But what I tell you is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:49.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Itachi did mention it, did he not?\NAbout his accomplice that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I am {\i1}that{\i0}  Madara Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:02.58,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything about Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:06.71,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose Itachi died\Nwithout realizing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:11.58,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!\NSuch things don't matter anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:13.58,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.91,0:01:17.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you will listen.\NYou need to hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:20.65,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your obligation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:23.75,english,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of the ninja world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:25.65,english,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of\Nthe Hidden Leaf Village...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.15,0:01:28.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And for your sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:32.71,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother risked everything.\NYou will know how Itachi Uchiha lived!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:44.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why Itachi implanted Amaterasu\Ninto your eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:51.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Itachi was determined to make sure\Nthat you and I would not meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You will understand why,\Nas well as everything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,when you hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:01.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who knew the truth about Itachi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:04.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,were Danzo of the Hidden Leaf,\Nthe Third Hokage,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:08.81,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and his advisors Homura and Koharu.\NJust those four.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:14.81,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Third Hokage died...\Nand now, there are only three aging folk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:21.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, those three will probably\Nnever reveal the abominable truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:25.75,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth about Itachi will fade\Ninto darkness forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:28.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is what Itachi wished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:36.88,english,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I know the truth\Nabout Itachi too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:43.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said earlier...\NItachi died without realizing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:46.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,However, he wanted to\Nmake doubly sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:49.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Itachi did not trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:53.51,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So just in case I did know the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:56.75,english,,0000,0000,0000,,he planned to silence me\Nwith the Amaterasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:01.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably anticipated I would show\Nmy Sharingan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:02.85,english,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:06.35,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:10.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this guy saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:14.95,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:17.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:20.58,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:25.75,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Think back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:32.25,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Think carefully and\Nremember about Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:48.51,english,,0000,0000,0000,,About your kind brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:04.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.88,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is it, right?\N{\i1}The place where Father works.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:14.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the headquarters of\N{\i1}the Hidden Leaf Police Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:17.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've always been curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:22.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is the Uchiha crest\N{\i1}on the police force logo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:24.51,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? You noticed that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:25.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who wouldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well...let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:36.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Simply put, it seems our ancestors formed\N{\i1}and organized this police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:41.85,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, they used our family crest\N{\i1}as the symbol of this organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From ages past,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.71,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}our clan has been entrusted\N{\i1}with the safety of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:52.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Uchiha crest reflects\N{\i1}the pride of our clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:57.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While its numbers have dwindled,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:01.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even today, nearly everyone in\N{\i1}the clan serves on Squad One
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.88,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and is dedicated to preserving\N{\i1}the peace and safety of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:11.21,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, only exceptional ninja are capable\N{\i1}of preventing crimes that ninja commit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father is great, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.18,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you going to work here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:19.75,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.25,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:27.11,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:30.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:32.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to take my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:39.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who would do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:43.35,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Foolish little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mangekyo Sharingan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Breathe slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:15.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:26.21,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if you do hate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:29.05,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what big brothers are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:37.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, Sasuke... Another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:30.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fate    \N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.81,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I took the liberty\Nof tying you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:45.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you weren't gonna stay still\Nand listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:54.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He... Itachi was my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:59.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed our parents...\NHe killed everyone in the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:02.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a Rogue Ninja...\NA member of the Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.81,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He was despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:09.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He was my target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:15.05,english,,0000,0000,0000,,that he annihilated\Nthe Uchiha clan that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:17.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And he deserted the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:19.88,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:24.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is what he was ordered\Nto do by the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:30.35,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the beginning of\Nthe truth about Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:32.75,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It was his mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:34.88,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:36.35,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That night,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:39.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Itachi killed his personal feelings\Nand fulfilled his mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've calmed down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:48.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.58,english,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to talk about Itachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:56.58,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I must take you back to the early days\Nwhen Hidden Leaf Village was founded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:00.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Itachi sacrificed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fate that has continued\Nsince ages past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:06.25,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He was sacrificed for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:08.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:09.18,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:15.75,english,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge problem rooted since the time\NHidden Leaf Village was founded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:18.71,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what determined Itachi's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:27.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long story,\Nbut everything I tell you is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:30.51,english,,0000,0000,0000,,On what basis should I believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:32.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're untrustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:36.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can show you\Nas proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:39.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's up to you whether\Nyou believe me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:43.71,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But you will hear me out until I finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:59.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine... So talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:04.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It all started more\Nthan 80 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:13.75,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The world was in turmoil.\NIt was the age of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:20.35,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Nations battled for power and\Nto increase their territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:23.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,During this age of war,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:27.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,ninjas consisted of individual clans\Nserving as armed units.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:32.65,english,,0000,0000,0000,,They were hired by various nations\Nto participate in the fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:40.81,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And among the many ninja clans,\Ntwo were feared as the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:45.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,One was us, the Uchiha clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:48.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And the other was known\Nas the Forest's Senju Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.51,0:11:53.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We of the Uchiha clan possessed\Nexceptional chakra and the Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:58.18,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Excelling in all types of warfare,\Nwe became known as a battle clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:03.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was born into the Uchiha clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:06.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,possessing chakra that\Nwas especially powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:11.21,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps the fact that I've lived\Nthis long is proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:15.18,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Back in those days,\Nall I did was battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:17.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,In an age defined by power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:20.75,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I sought to become ever stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:23.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and killed my friends and\Neven my younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:30.55,english,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, I came into possession\Nof the perfect Mangekyo Sharingan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.95,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and became the leader of the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:38.81,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And using that power,\NI fought the Senju clan countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:44.75,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It was inevitable that I face Hashirama,\Nthe leader of the Senju clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:50.81,english,,0000,0000,0000,,"Wood Style" Hashirama Senju,\Nthe future first Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:53.75,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who stood at\Nthe top of the ninja world...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:56.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one I respected most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:08.25,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Senju clan, led by Hashirama\Nwho became the First Hokage,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:13.11,english,,0000,0000,0000,,was feared and respected\Nby all the other clans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:17.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Senju moved,\Nso did the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:21.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Our clan was probably the only clan\Nable to compete with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:23.88,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If a nation hired the Senju,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:25.81,english,,0000,0000,0000,,the opposing nation would hire\Nthe Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:27.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We were like rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.35,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I went up against Hashirama,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.65,english,,0000,0000,0000,,the more my name became known\Nas well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:40.05,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To get close to the top...\N{\i1}to measure my abilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:43.85,english,,0000,0000,0000,,To heighten your reputation...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:47.05,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You took your younger brother's eyes\Njust for that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:49.35,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I did take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:55.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But I needed power in order\Nto protect the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:57.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:14:02.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. As the Uchiha name spread,\Nits enemies increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:06.65,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a necessary sacrifice\Nto protect the clan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:11.21,english,,0000,0000,0000,,during the fierce fighting with the Senju,\Nand the other clans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:14.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It was not for my fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.35,english,,0000,0000,0000,,My younger brother was\Nin total agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:22.05,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and offered his eyes to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:31.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day,\Nthe Senju clan offered a truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.81,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Uchiha accepted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:39.95,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, in both clans,\Nhad grown weary of the fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.35,english,,0000,0000,0000,,that had dragged on for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,They had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:50.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the only one who opposed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:55.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Where has all the hate gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:59.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,For what purpose had my brother\Nsacrificed himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:09.18,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Uchiha and Senju are\Nlike oil and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:11.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help fearing that in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:15.65,english,,0000,0000,0000,,the Uchiha clan would come to\Nbe oppressed by the Senju clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:24.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,However...everyone in the Uchiha clan\Nwanted a truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:29.75,english,,0000,0000,0000,,As their leader, I had no choice\Nbut to go along with their wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:38.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shortly thereafter, the ninja alliance\Nsigned a pact with the Land of Fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:40.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,which had sought dominion\Nover the territories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:45.38,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The secure one nation, one village system\Nwas formed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:48.71,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and became the Land of Fire and\Nthe Village Hidden in the Leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:54.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Other countries adopted\Nthe one nation, one village system.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:58.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And subsequently,\Nthe fires of war were extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.85,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Momentary peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.95,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But due to a certain incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:06.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,the Hidden Leaf Village quickly\Ndescended into turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:08.85,english,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:13.95,english,,0000,0000,0000,,A fight...for the First Hokage's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:19.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, the first to occupy\Nthat seat was Hashirama Senju.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:23.18,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Land of Fire and\Nthe entire clan chose Hashirama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.75,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It was inevitable
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:28.51,english,,0000,0000,0000,,that the Uchiha's hold on\Nthe reins of power would loosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:34.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that the Uchiha\Nshould take leadership...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:38.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That we should confront Hashirama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:43.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one, not even from\Nthe Uchiha clan, supported me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.51,0:16:47.88,english,,0000,0000,0000,,My subordinates, who did not wish\Nto light the fires of war,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:50.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,were unsympathetic and betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:59.85,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I was accused of acting\Nout of greed and self-interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:04.18,english,,0000,0000,0000,,They scorned me as\Na selfish brother
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:06.81,english,,0000,0000,0000,,who stole his younger brother's eyes\Nin order to save his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:11.18,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What brother would willfully\Nhurt his younger brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:16.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...I just wanted to\Nprotect the Uchiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.51,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I left the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:23.41,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:29.68,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I became an avenger and declared\Nwar on the Hidden Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:47.58,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:52.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,At that place which became known\Nas the Final Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:55.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I was said...to have died there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Hashirama believed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.75,0:18:06.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And everyone forgot about me...\NHistory forgot about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:10.31,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashirama's younger brother\Nwho became the Second Hokage
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:12.85,english,,0000,0000,0000,,was determined that there would\Nnever be a traitor like me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:17.48,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So, as proof of his trust, he granted\Nthe Uchiha a special position...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:21.75,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And he created\Nthe Hidden Leaf Police Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:28.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This was to further distance the Uchiha\Nfrom the reins of government.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:31.71,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, it was a way to keep\Na close eye on the entire clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:35.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There were Uchiha members\Nwho realized this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:39.68,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Members who wanted to carry\Non my rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:44.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But...it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:46.61,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Time passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:48.98,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Senju clan solidified\Nits hold on power
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:52.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Uchiha fell to\Nbecoming Senju dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:56.28,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And what I predicted came to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:19:01.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain other incident sealed\NUchiha's figurative demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.45,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:11.08,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The attack of the Nine-Tailed Fox Demon\N16 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:17.01,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:21.11,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nine-Tails can only be tamed\Nand controlled
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,by the ocular powers of the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:26.85,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The higher-ups of Hidden Leaf Village\Nperceived the Uchiha
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:29.65,english,,0000,0000,0000,,to be behind this attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:33.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a natural occurrence,\Na natural calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:35.68,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Uchiha had nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:40.15,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet suspicion fell on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:44.85,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That the Uchiha had revolted\Nand sought to take power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.78,english,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result,\Nthe Uchiha was put under
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:51.91,english,,0000,0000,0000,,the strict surveillance of\Nthe Anbu Black Ops,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:55.88,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and they were forced to relocate\Nto the outskirts of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0: